<br>
 Grieg fight is a blast. But you really can't do the normal Big Tank Whack Mob Nuts Everyone Heal Him technique used for 90% of mobs.<br>
<br>
 Our 1st fight we dropped him maybe 5-10% at best. Went in totally blind and got ripped apart. Second fight wasn't much better but we figured out what we wanted to do. 3rd fight we refined the strat a little and picked a good spot to fight, got him to about 10-20%. 4th fight same spot better execution no deaths. <p><B><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6122>Grimmlokk</a>, Forlorn</B> <BR>
